node.text:
CHECK IT OUT: We have the official guest brewery list for Nate Soroko's celebration of life. Friends and family will be getting together at our barrel warehouse on the 31st from 1PM-4PM to have some extremely choice beverages and toast to a truly extraordinary person. Tickets are available online now, and everyone who was lucky enough to know and love this industry icon is welcome to attend.
—
This event will benefit a local San Diego non-profit that provides culinary apprenticeships to people in need of a fresh start and a career.

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Modern Times Beer on July 22, 2021. May be an image of drink.

node.text: PRESALE BEER: Metaverse. A Portland-brewed hybrid of haze and West Coast flavors, this 7.7% IPA is laden with Bru-1, Citra, and Idaho-7 hops for a lovely bouquet of pineapple, tangerine, and subtle pine. It’s a super-delicious collision of IPA styles that we think you’re going to be glad you experienced. You'll be able to secure your allotment in Saturday's online presale.

node.text: NOW HIRING: General Manager in San Diego. We're currently on a quest to find a GM for all San Diego locations. This is a big position that requires maintaining/increasing current levels of radness at our tasting rooms along with recruitment, customer experience, and management of the leadership team. If you’ve got the requisite experience and a deep, enduring love of delicious beer & coffee, we'd totally suggest checking out details and applying via moderntimesbeer.com/careers.

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Modern Times Beer on July 21, 2021. May be an image of drink.

node.text:
PRESALE BEER: Mist Dragon with Galaxy. Conceived in collaboration with Humble Sea, this 5.6% beer is a glorious union of two disparate realms. We started with a hazy IPA malt-bill and fermented with lager yeast before hopping with Galaxy and Perle. The result is a foggy lager sporting aromas of citrus, peach, and passion fruit, with a pillowy soft mouthfeel and lager-like finish. It’s a majestic new beast and a testament to the combined powers of weird minds.
—
Cans will be available in Saturday's online presale, all of the information for which will go out via email newsletter Thursday evening. Sign up at moderntimesbeer.com, if you'd like to receive it.

node.text: PRESALE BEER: Pool Zone. At a cool 3.2% ABV and 100 calories per 12oz can, it’s a summertime beverage no-brainer. You can get all the juicy details via our most recent blog post.

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Modern Times Beer on July 19, 2021. May be an image of drink.

node.text:
PRESALE BEER: DDH Finally Open in Anaheim. Leisuretown is coming up on its one-year anniversary (what?!), and we’re celebrating by doubling down on the DIPA that celebrated its grand opening. Hopped with Mosaic, Citra, Strata, and Idaho-7, this 8% birthday party in a can will lavish your taste buds with a dazzling array of fruity, dank, and tropical notes.
—
You'll be able to secure your allotment in Saturday's online presale. All the details will go out via our email newsletter, which you can sign up for at moderntimesbeer.com.

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Modern Times Beer on July 18, 2021. May be an image of drink and outdoors.

node.text: We love Brain Vacation, and we don't care who knows it. This enchantingly spritzy tropical gose is loaded with pineapple, passion fruit, guava, and orange, making for an unparalleled 3.3% beverage experience. If you haven't made it official yet, you can snag a 6-er at our spots, as well as at fine beverage retailers throughout our regular realms of distribution.

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Modern Times Beer on July 17, 2021. May be an image of outdoors.

node.text: Whatever your plans are today--whether you're in for a good-old-fashioned float  or mowing the lawn--you can totally snag cans of this insanely delicious West Coast-style IPA at our spots. It's virtually guaranteed to serve you well, wherever your day takes you.

PACKAGING TEAM APPRECIATION! These tireless, multitasking super-humans run 2 super delicate machines, ripping through 200 barrels (at least) per day. That means packing up thousands of cases so that beer can be delivered to all your faces, fresh. We are eternally grateful for this hardworking bunch, and if you've ever enjoyed cracking an MT can, you should be too.
--
From our Packaging Manager: 
Where do we even begin with this team... These folks are the are one of the main reasons we are still operating as a company; knocking out pack plans and packaging day and night to meet orders and trucking needs. This team has overcome tremendous odds and maintained a 200+ bbl average throughout the entire pandemic shutdown, while adhering to strict quality & food safety guidelines. But that's not all...They learned a brand new case packer machine--top to bottom--and also kept up with our raw material warehousing (40 pallets on average per week). To say these folks are superheroes is an understatement. Cheers to you all, Packaging Team.

node.text:
TICKETS ARE ON SALE! If you'd like to join us in Celebrating the Life of Nate Soroko on 7/31, you are totally welcome to. We'll be pouring some excellent beverages alongside a bunch of decidedly tight guest breweries while we cheers to a singularly wonderful human being. Your $20 ticket gets you a memorial taster glass, with which you can get 8 4oz pours. Friends and family will gather from 1PM-4PM at our San Diego barrel warehouse, the Fortress of Raditude. Tickets can be found in our online store, or by following the profile link.
--
This event will benefit a local non-profit that provides culinary apprenticeships to people in need of a career and a fresh start.

node.text: ANNIVERSARY RADNESS! This weekend, MT8! (8% DIPA with Riwaka, Nelson, & Mosaic hops, & Sauvignon Blanc grape dust) is hitting all tasting rooms as an extra special birthday treat. We'll also be pouring Mega Devil's Teeth with Coconut, Cocoa, Maple, & Almonds, plus a few other tasty little surprises. We'd love it if you swung by our spots for a toast.

node.text: HEADS-UP, CALIFORNIA: You can totally get the Ultimate 6-Pack Mixed Pack delivered right to your door. We've somewhat recently forayed into the realm of 12 oz-ers, so we've made easy to get a sampling with this case of killer beers: Abaddon (Helles lager), Brain Vacation (spritzy tropical gose), Sundiver (Mexican lager), and Dungeon Map (West Coast IPA). Head to the online store (moderntimesmmerch.com) to put in your order, if you so desire.
